Swing Trade Setups

Setups

  • Breakout Setups - IWM, MDY & SPY or QQQ > 50MA
  • Pullback Setups - Market (all3) > 50MA - HOT SECTOR - Consolidation - Up 20% Month, 30% Quarter, 50% Six Months
  • IPO Setups - Market (all3) > 50MA - Low share float - Enter after correction, consolidation, hot industry
  • Industry Momentum Setups - Any Market - Leading Industry -> Find top stocks -> Enter breakout/pullback
  • Earnings Gap Setups - Right after earnings release look for base on VWAP and take position
  • Short Squeeze Setups - Near 52wk highs with catalyst or Near 52wk lows on a correction - Markets up
  • Huge Volume Setups - Russel uptrend and IWN > 10, 50, & 200 MA. 10x volume can last few weeks or consolidate
  • Bearish Setups - 2/3 IWN, MDY, SPY or QQQ < 10 & 50SMA. Best when market is in correction mode 8-10%
  • Relative Strength Setups - Stocks with high momentum best performers 3-6mths. Correction making new highs.
  • Mean-Reversion Setups - Best in range bound markets (1/3 index are up rest < 50SMA) - Long declining 50SMA end at top.
